feed.title: Condo Water Monitor 1.0
feed.description:
This is an Ultra Sonic range finder monitoring the ground water level to prevent future flooding.  I am using an Arduino to collect the information from the sensor and a Fonera wireless router to upload the data here.  Here are some photos of this project:
